{"id":465,"parent_id":454,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":465,"title":"Job 11","subtitle":"","short_title":"Job","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 11"],[".studySummary",["i","Zophar asks, Canst thou by searching find out God?—Zophar says that the hope of the wicked will fade away as though it had died."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.1","order":"02.19.011.33452"},["b","1"],"Then answered Zophar the Naamathite, and said,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.2","order":"02.19.011.33453"},["b","2"],"Should not the multitude of words be answered? and should a man full of talk be justified?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.3","order":"02.19.011.33454"},["b","3"],"Should thy lies make men hold their peace? and when thou mockest, shall no man make thee ashamed?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.4","order":"02.19.011.33455"},["b","4"],"For thou hast said, My doctrine",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"pure"],", and I am clean in thine eyes."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.5","order":"02.19.011.33456"},["b","5"],"But oh that God would speak, and open his lips against thee;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.6","order":"02.19.011.33457"},["b","6"],"And that he would shew thee the secrets of wisdom, that",["i","they are"],"double to that which is! Know therefore that God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"exacteth"],"of thee",["i","less"],"than thine iniquity",["i","deserveth."]],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.7","order":"02.19.011.33458"},["b","7"],"Canst thou by searching find out God? canst thou find out the Almighty unto perfection?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.8","order":"02.19.011.33459"},["b","8"],["i","It is"],"as high as heaven; what canst thou do? deeper than hell; what canst thou know?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.9","order":"02.19.011.33460"},["b","9"],"The measure thereof",["i","is"],"longer than the earth, and broader than the sea."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.10","order":"02.19.011.33461"},["b","10"],"If he cut off, and shut up, or gather together, then who can hinder him?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.11","order":"02.19.011.33462"},["b","11"],"For he knoweth vain men: he seeth wickedness also; will he not then consider",["i","it?"]],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.12","order":"02.19.011.33463"},["b","12"],"For",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"vain"],"man would be wise, though man be born",["i","like"],"a wild ass’s colt."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.13","order":"02.19.011.33464"},["b","13"],"If thou prepare thine heart, and stretch out thine hands toward him;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.14","order":"02.19.011.33465"},["b","14"],"If iniquity",["i","be"],"in thine hand, put it far away, and let not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"wickedness"],"dwell in thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"tabernacles"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.15","order":"02.19.011.33466"},["b","15"],"For then shalt thou lift up thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"face"],"without spot; yea, thou shalt be steadfast, and shalt not fear:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.16","order":"02.19.011.33467"},["b","16"],"Because thou shalt forget",["i","thy"],"misery,",["i","and"],"remember",["i","it"],"as waters",["i","that"],"pass away:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.17","order":"02.19.011.33468"},["b","17"],"And",["i","thine"],"age shall be clearer than the noonday; thou shalt shine forth, thou shalt be as the morning."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.18","order":"02.19.011.33469"},["b","18"],"And thou shalt be secure, because there is hope; yea, thou shalt dig",["i","about thee, and"],"thou shalt take thy rest in safety."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.19","order":"02.19.011.33470"},["b","19"],"Also thou shalt lie down, and none shall make",["i","thee"],"afraid; yea, many shall make suit unto thee."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.20","order":"02.19.011.33471"},["b","20"],"But the eyes of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"wicked"],"shall fail, and they shall not escape, and their hope",["i","shall be as"],"the giving up of the ghost."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.4a","order":"02.19.011.33472"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.47"},"2 Ne. 9:47"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.6a","order":"02.19.011.33474"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.14"},"D&C 38:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.12a","order":"02.19.011.33476"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.28"},"2 Ne. 9:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.14a","order":"02.19.011.33478"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/38.8"},"Alma 38:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.14b","order":"02.19.011.33480"},["b","14b"],["span.small","HEB"],"tents."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.15a","order":"02.19.011.33482"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/22.26.23,26-27"},"Job 22:26 (23, 26–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/11.20a","order":"02.19.011.33484"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/122.9"},"D&C 122:9"],"."]]}
